OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCloudy with patchy rain to start
OL,7,FThursday but gradually turning
OL,8,Fbrighter. Very warm on Friday and
OL,9,FSaturday, with sunny periods, although
OL,10,Fsome thundery showers are possible at
OL,11,Ftimes.
